  toplevel    alpha      beta

|----------|----------|----------------------------|
  frame of   frame of
  toplevel    alpha

|----------|---------------------------------------|
  frame of
  toplevel
@end example
@caption{Scheme stack segment after returning from @func{delta},
@func{beta}, @func{alpha}.}
@end float

